text.section:
All receipts designated for the Grant Fund shall be placed in the Grant Fund held by the Department and administered by the Trust, including:
Moneys appropriated by the State to the Grant Fund;
Premiums, fees, and payments on reimbursement of grants, where required;
Income from investments that the State Treasurer, on instruction of the Department, makes for the Department under this subtitle; and
Any other moneys made available to the Grant Fund.
